The  '''Cones Series''' is a series of 87 abstract paintings by Turkish artist [[Burhan Doğançay]], executed between 1986 and 1995 and featuring [[cone (geometry)|cones]].

In almost all of the paintings in the series the [[collage]] and [[fumage]] techniques are applied.

